@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave
@employeeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007

@employeeAuth = Basic employee@company.com:123456
@managerAuth = Basic manager@company.com:123456

# Setelah step 1.1 berhasil, copy ID dari response lalu paste di sini
@leaveRequestId = paste-created-id-here


### 1.1 - Create Business Draft - Single Approval
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests
Authorization: {{employeeAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Reason": "Case 1 - Single approval then approve",
  "Employee_ID": "{{employeeId}}",
  "RequestDate": "2026-05-05T09:00:00Z"
}


### 1.2 - Read Created Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeAuth}}


### 1.3 - Submit Leave Request
### Expected:
### Status = InProgress
### RequestNumber generated
### LeaveApprovals contains 1 row:
### StepNo = 1, Decision = Pending, IsCurrent = true
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.submit
Authorization: {{employeeAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### 1.4 - Read After Submit
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeAuth}}


### 1.5 - Approve Leave Request
### Expected:
### Status = Approved
### IsClosed = true
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Comments": "Case 1 approved"
}


### 1.6 - Read Approved Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeAuth}}